eus strain on April 9 and has not played since then, including missing the first-round playoffs against the Indiana Pacers.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.598123660955623e-44, \"text\": \"Indiana Pacers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bucks lost that series\\u00a04-2\\u00a0in the end.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The day of Game 4 in Indiana, that was the first time I was able to jog on my body weight since April 9,\\\" Antetokounmpo said in May.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"score\": 0.9999398444701677, \"rank\": 5.934359913077323e-05, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, I think I tried my best to come back to help my teammates.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's kind of hard to see them being out there and not being able to help them.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just could not.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did all the tests I had to do, like these protocols you have to follow and have to check the boxes, and I wasn't even close (to) checking the boxes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hot